honest.

00:03:26.609 --> 00:03:31.709
I knew they treated scalp conditions and hair,
but I didn't really know a lot.

00:03:31.709 --> 00:03:37.909
I did a bit of research on Shuna and got a
little bit but it was great.

00:03:37.909 --> 00:03:39.969
She worked totally round me to come.

